Usage
Running the Application:
To run the application using your webcam:

bash
Copy code
python main.py
You will be prompted to define the zones interactively. Once the zones are defined, the system will start detecting raised hands and displaying the coffee requests. The requests will disappear after 5 seconds.

Running with a Video File:
To process a video file instead of the webcam, pass the video path as an argument:

bash
Copy code
python main.py --video_path "path/to/your/video.mp4"

Key Commands:
Using mouse left button you can select and add zone for specific name/ person
Press r to start processing the video after defining the zones.
Press q to quit the application.
